Package com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.server.oplock

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IOperationLock<C>
    Represents a lock for an owning context of arbitrary type and a lock target.
    IOperationLockTargetListener<C>
    Represents a lock target listener that receives notifications of an appearing or disappearing IOperationLockTarget in an AbstractOperationLockManager instance.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractOperationLock<C>
    An abstract lock implementation which supports basic methods of IOperationLock.
    AbstractOperationLockManager<C extends java.io.Serializable>
    An abstract superclass of IOperationLockManager providing common methods.
    OperationLockInfo<C extends java.io.Serializable>
    Contains all information about an operation lock which should be presented on an administrative interface.
    ReentrantOperationLock<C>
    Represents a reentrant lock that can be acquired and released in a balanced fashion multiple times by the same context.
    ReentrantOperationLockManager<C extends java.io.Serializable>
    An AbstractOperationLockManager implementation that uses ReentrantOperationLocks.
